title: 21 Naturals - Blue Angel { Pluck my Flower - 09.30.2016 } 1080p
description:
Blue Angel floats down to earth to smell the flowers, and another desire catches her interest. Joss Lescaf walks over to this heavenly creature with a substantial offering, worthy of the gods. This mortal man drives his monstrous shaft into the angelic beauty, with her cries of pleasure echoing up into the skies above. Did she become a fallen angel in the process, and was her sweet flower plucked?
